name: Mechmate Factory – Season 01
description:
|Mechmate Factory – Season 01| 
Utility: Owner/HODLer of this factory will receive a Mechmate when it drops during the season.  
Factory production will halt after the season ends. Production line is transferable when factory is resold in the secondary market. (New owner will receive the next drops) / Zone: Desert / Income +1 MM Token/cycle.
